Don't you like her?

01:45:31.034 --> 01:45:37.974
You are blushing
you rascal, you sweetie pie

01:45:38.334 --> 01:45:41.042
Call her
Call her

01:45:41.100 --> 01:45:43.774
Sir
Sir?

01:45:45.401 --> 01:45:47.312
