- Get lost where?

01:45:54.700 --> 01:45:55.770
Sir, come with me
Let's go home

01:45:56.000 --> 01:45:58.310
I'm not going
back to my house

01:46:00.801 --> 01:46:02.212
Superb

01:46:03.334 --> 01:46:04.438
One large

01:46:04.500 --> 01:46:06.309
